						<div class="postbody">There was an Atari ST cartridge called Spectre that used ROM chips desoldered from a Macintosh Plus to run Mac OS.<br /><br />But the I/O of the Genesis was so different from that of, say, the Mac that games were rarely ported between the two.</div>

